## 🔐 Cryptographic Software Disclosure

This product includes the **OpenSSL FIPS 140-3 Validated Module (fips.dll)**, version **3.1.2**,
as distributed by **The OpenSSL Project**.

The module is redistributed **in its original, unmodified form**, along with its official Security Policy.

> ⚠️ **Disclaimer**:
> Although this product incorporates a FIPS 140-3 validated module, **this product and Wesley Atwell**
> **have not been independently certified or validated** by **NIST** or the **CMVP**.
> Use of the module does **not** imply FIPS-validated compliance for this product.

---

### 🔍 Module Details

* **Name**: OpenSSL FIPS Provider Module
* **Version**: 3.1.2
* **Website**: [https://www.openssl.org](https://www.openssl.org)
* **License**: Apache License 2.0
* **FIPS Certificate**: A3548
* **Security Policy**: *"OpenSSL FIPS 140-3 Security Policy, Version 1.0, December 29, 2023"*

---

### ⚠️ Important Redistribution Terms

* **Redistribution of fips.dll is permitted** only if it is:

  * Whole and unmodified,
  * Distributed with the complete, original FIPS Security Policy document.
* **Modification** of the binary or configuration files will invalidate the FIPS 140-3 validation.
* **No endorsement**: Wesley Atwell is not a FIPS validation authority or certified distributor.

> ⚠️ **Warning**:
> Redistribution is allowed under the original OpenSSL terms, but **no warranties, guarantees, or FIPS endorsements** are implied.

